        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down.</hi> | Beckenham | <hi rend="print">Kent. S.E.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>Ap. 9<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></date>
                    <salute>My dear Gray</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I had heard of, &amp; given, the case of the difference in colour of the sexes of Lemur, but I was not at all aware of the great variability of the male &amp; stability of the female.<ref target="#foot.f2"/> Therefore many thanks.</p>
<p>Yours very sincerely | Ch Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="tnotes">
                <note xml:id="tnote.n1">0.1 Beckenham] <hi rend="italic">before del</hi> ‘<hi rend="italic">Bromley.</hi>’ </note>
            </div>

            
            
            
            
        </div>

        

        

